00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:54.000
Just kidding!

00:00:55.040 --> 00:00:57.820
It's true that you'll need time to heal.

00:00:58.260 --> 00:01:00.070
But just a moment ago,

00:01:00.070 --> 00:01:04.060
