00:12:03.970 --> 00:12:07.920
Steel is fixing itself to my body!

00:12:08.650 --> 00:12:10.920
Could it be that my body...

00:12:14.150 --> 00:12:15.890
My body...

00:12:16.140 --> 00:12:18.560
Has it turned into a magnet?!

00:12:22.630 --> 00:12:24.980
Ow!

00:12:28.810 --> 00:12:31.490
Th-This magnetism... Could it be a new Stand?

00:12:31.990 --> 00:12:35.110
But why? Why can't I see the Stand?

00:12:35.110 --> 00:12:39.030
