at me without a Stand around?

00:12:41.860 --> 00:12:43.910
C-Could it be...

00:12:43.910 --> 00:12:48.820
Has the shock from that rock
turned my body into a magnet?

00:12:52.530 --> 00:12:54.050
I-I can't get loose...

00:12:54.310 --> 00:12:58.800
O-Oh, no! The escalator is made of steel!

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:03.310
And the magnetism is getting
stronger by the minute!

00:13:11.380 --> 00:13:12.780
What?!

00:13:13.210 --> 00:13:16.880
H-Hey, you! The lady in the miniskirt!

00:13:16.880 --> 00:13:18.690
This is trouble!

00:13:18.690 --> 00:13:21.990
Your chain's gotten tangled
around my hands and body,

00:13:21.990 --> 00:13:24.290
and it's getting dragged into the ramp!

00:13:24.590 --> 00:13:28.710
Push the emergency stop button
at the bottom of the escalator!

00:13:28.710 --> 00:13:32.030
At this rate, your chains will get dragged in,

00:13:32.030 --> 00:13:34.720
