00:13:35.550 --> 00:13:38.670
H-Hey, are you listening?

00:13:45.670 --> 00:13:49.020
Enjoy, Joseph Joestar.

00:13:49.020 --> 00:13:54.030
Wh-What?! D-Don't tell me you...

00:13:54.730 --> 00:13:57.630
