00:14:02.260 --> 00:14:04.950
Bastet

00:14:03.060 --> 00:14:04.950
Mariah

00:14:05.370 --> 00:14:07.830
D-Don't tell me you...

00:14:07.830 --> 00:14:10.080
You're the Stand user?!

00:14:10.150 --> 00:14:17.320
Rumble                                       Rumble

00:14:11.980 --> 00:14:16.950
