00:15:46.350 --> 00:15:49.350
The stop button works just fine!

00:15:49.350 --> 00:15:52.980
Hey, are you from the hotel?

00:15:53.840 --> 00:15:57.530
Could you sign off on the inspection? Right here.

00:15:58.670 --> 00:16:01.650
What are you talking about, Mr. Joestar?!

00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:05.780
The enemy. I'm under the
spell of an enemy Stand.

00:16:05.780 --> 00:16:08.160
My body is like a magnet now...

00:16:12.270 --> 00:16:16.730
She turned me into a magnet!
Steel sticks to me!

00:16:16.730 --> 00:16:18.340
Pull this thing off me!

00:16:18.340 --> 00:16:23.430
And the magnetic force
keeps getting stronger...

00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:30.110
It's her! That woman is the user!

00:16:30.110 --> 00:16:30.620
What?

00:16:30.620 --> 00:16:32.550
Catch that woman!

00:16:32.550 --> 00:16:35.430
We have to stop her magnetism at once,

00:16:35.430 --> 00:16:37.900
or it'll get so strong,
I won't be able to move!

00:16:37.900 --> 00:16:40.570
Let's go get Jotaro and Polnareff!
They're waiting outside.

00:16:40.570 --> 00:16:41.820
What?!

00:16:42.260 --> 00:16:45.310
