00:17:12.630 --> 00:17:14.060
I'm going in.

00:17:14.700 --> 00:17:16.660
My life depends on it!

00:17:16.660 --> 00:17:19.190
I'm going to catch that woman, no matter what!

00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:19.190
Mr. Joestar?!

00:17:27.090 --> 00:17:28.660
The old man's not here yet?

00:17:31.300 --> 00:17:36.700
Yeah. Avdol went to get him,
and he's not back, either...

00:17:37.870 --> 00:17:38.920
Could it be...

00:17:39.280 --> 00:17:41.000
They secretly...

00:17:42.580 --> 00:17:45.910
