00:18:15.750 --> 00:18:19.400
But as I expected, most of the stalls are in use.

00:18:18.080 --> 00:18:19.400
Shh!

00:18:19.400 --> 00:18:21.250
Oh, shh...

00:18:21.810 --> 00:18:28.680
Sorry. But I-I don't know...
Which one is she in?

00:18:28.930 --> 00:18:31.120
She has amazing legs.

00:18:31.120 --> 00:18:32.450
H-Her legs?

00:18:32.450 --> 00:18:34.670
Yes! Look for those legs!

00:18:34.670 --> 00:18:36.870
You'll know right away if you spot them.

00:18:36.870 --> 00:18:39.440
W-We're going to look in?

00:18:50.990 --> 00:18:52.370
That's not it.

00:18:52.760 --> 00:18:53.910
Or these...

00:18:54.180 --> 00:18:55.490
